{{#> layout appName="NestJS App" tagline="Email Verification" supportEmail="support@example.com" year="2024"}}
<h1>Verify Your Email Address</h1>

<p>Hi {{name}},</p>

<p>Thank you for signing up! To complete your registration and start using your account, please verify your email address by clicking the button below.</p>

<div class="text-center mb-30">
    <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="btn">Verify Email</a>
</div>

<p>This verification link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons.</p>

<p>If the button above doesn't work, you can copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
<p style="word-break: break-all; color: #666; font-size: 14px;">{{verificationLink}}</p>

<div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #495057;">
        <strong>Didn't create an account?</strong> If you didn't create an account with us, you can safely ignore this email.
    </p>
</div>

<p>Once verified, you'll have full access to all our features and services.</p>

<p>
    Best regards,<br>
    The {{appName}} Team
</p>
{{/layout}}
